      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（俺達は、海沿いのキャンプ場に来ていた）\n（星見市のタウン誌でレジャースポットを紹介する仕事だ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(We’re visiting a campsite along the seashore.)\n(It’s for a tourism job for the Hoshimi City town magazine.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.766666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（キャンプのことを綴った遙子さんのブログが）\n（編集者の目に留まり、記事のモデルに指名されたのだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Haruko-san’s camping blog caught the eye of the editor‚)\n(and she was picked to model for an article.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.633333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、{user}君\nこっちのお肉、もういい感じだよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ {user}?\nThis meat looks cooked to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.533333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_01_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "あとこっちのタマネギも\nお野菜もちゃんと食べなきゃダメだよ？",
